The Glenn Beck Radio Show SEP-25-2014 THURS




The Glenn Beck Program


 The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET 



        
      
      Mike Rowe joins Glenn & sings opera 9/25/14



Thursday, September 25, 2014 11:27 AM



Glenn talks about President Obama still acting like a high schooler,

  discusses why Mayor de Blasio is dangerous around animals and 

  Senator James Inhofe joins the show to share his perspective on 
       terrorism and the UN.  

   Also, Mike Rowe joins Glenn in studio to sing opera, 
     discuss an odd museum in Missouri and the evolution of television.

           That and much more on The Glenn Beck Program!
